  "detailed_description": "*** This game is only available in Traditional Chinese ***<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >梦想当出色的模特儿、演员、歌星？</h2>海量广告、歌曲、戏剧通告，让你体验丰富的艺界人生！<br>角色事件错综复杂，约<strong>40种事业与感情结局</strong>，你能得到最高的荣誉吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542280/extras/4c4f15383e0c7cd1a2dd1c6d3b8b5a3f.avif?t=1648688561\" width=600 height=252 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精彩的行程安排</h2>为自己安排每日行程，家居、训练、休闲、恋爱、接通告，努力成为更好的自己。<br>游戏提供<strong>60余种行程安排</strong>，每天都有不同感动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542280/extras/1206f01f702f33a7b5d68900cb8fbd1c.avif?t=1648688561\" width=400 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >甜蜜恋爱</h2>天王？大导演？医生？富商？ 与男主角们相识相知，展开甜蜜约会与恋爱，<strong>7个感情结局</strong>等你攻略！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542280/extras/5805e5db72bf261142e7a205e7620589.avif?t=1648688561\" width=600 height=450 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真实演艺环境</h2>上综艺节目、尝试逗趣的小动画或竞赛，这是明星都得接受的挑战唷！<br>更多演艺圈人士和你互动，打造更真实的演艺环境。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542280/extras/e18f1d9e29927d091ecb9a55de55e372.avif?t=1648688561\" width=600 height=450 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索城市 寻找下一个机会</h2>探索城市地图，为自己寻找适合的通告、唱片公司，以及各种特殊机会！<br>也可闲逛休息，体验明星的休闲生活。<br>常常到处晃晃，有时还可获得意外惊喜和奇遇~<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542280/extras/9480c241708a63a7a7f2fbc6e1e69835.avif?t=1648688561\" width=600 height=258 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NP鸡饲养欢乐无穷</h2>游戏中藏着可爱的NP鸡，好好饲养，也会有它自己的结局唷！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1542280/extras/e6bf79779ca0b6c186a5c1ac564e5a02.avif?t=1648688561\" width=138 height=108 /></span>",
